Class Sitefinity

class

Sitefinity

classdesc

The constructor of the Sitefinity JavaScript SDK. This is the entry point for the SDK.

property

{Object} authentication - The authentication object used for authenticating to Sitefinity. See Authentication

param

An object containing configuration options for the Setup object.

param

Your service url that points to the configured instance of Sitefinity service.

param

The ID of the site, for which the query will be executed.

param

The global handlers for request execution

param

The success handler.

param

The failure handler.
